                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13411923" author="ratha" created="Wed, 11 Jul 2012 20:12:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached a patch to avoid NPE..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fix;&lt;br/&gt;
If the resulted xpath evaluation returns null, lets assign an empty string ,so we will get &quot;URISyntaxException&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please go through the patch and commit...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13710098" author="hiranya" created="Tue, 16 Jul 2013 19:09:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I did a different but simpler fix. Basically if the XPath returns null, we treat the result as empty string. Added a test case to verify the fix too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13710180" author="hudson" created="Tue, 16 Jul 2013 20:20:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;SUCCESS: Integrated in Synapse - Trunk #4616 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Synapse%20-%20Trunk/4616/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Synapse%20-%20Trunk/4616/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
Fixing &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-889&quot; title=&quot;Null pointer exception is thrown, if xpath expression doesn&amp;#39;t match with the property&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SYNAPSE-889&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SYNAPSE-889&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; If the XPath expression evaluates to null in a RewriteAction, treat the result as if it was an empty string. Added a test case to verify the fix. (hiranya: rev 1503835)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/synapse/trunk/java/modules/core/src/main/java/org/apache/synapse/mediators/transform/url/RewriteAction.java&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/synapse/trunk/java/modules/core/src/test/java/org/apache/synapse/mediators/transform/url/URLRewriteMediatorTest.java&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
